name: Vitamin Coin
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: Vitamin Coin (VITC) is focused on living healthily, both mentally and physically. Unlike many other cryptocurrencies which are focused on financial value, VITC seeks to build and cultivate something that gives personal value. This is the central guiding principle of our project and community development.
